---
title: Bruschetta Bocconcini Bowls with Crispy Garlic Croutons
description: We've taken the classic Italian antipasto and made it a meal for two! Baked garlic croutons are tossed with spinach and juicy tomatoes, then topped with creamy bocconcini. A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set for date night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-a-la-bruschetta-et-aux-bocconcinis-604a6599.jpg
